Machine Demo

Machine Demo is a competition for startups with products that focus on innovation in hardware technology.
I created a brand that celebrated the physical aspect of the startups products. 

Iterations

The goal was to create a 'Machine' logo that looked like some of the
products that were being presented on the stage. After playing around with a lot of iterations 
I found an icon and logotype that fully represented the concept. 

Trophy Design

The competition also needed a trophy designed. Using the 3D build software SketchUp I designed a render of the logo as trophy. We had these made using molds and a sustainable concrete replacement material to make the trophy for the winner.
